        "subject": "LU-1593 test: use multiop_bg_pause in sanity test 34h",
        "message": "LU-1593 test: use multiop_bg_pause in sanity test 34h\n\nUse multiop_bg_pause instead of multiop & in sanity 34h to make\nsure multiop is running by the time the timeout is started.\nAlso sync dirty data from dd in case writeback holds page locks\nand delay truncate operation.\n\nSigned-off-by: Johann Lombardi <johann.lombardi@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3317cbc34826beca0aa4fb79c639d4861747a366\n"
      },
